{
  "texts": [
    "The potential impact of this framework is multifold, as it can enhance the usefulness of AI, assess possible new scientific understanding encoded in machines, and aid in educational programs.",
    "Future research directions include refining the methodology for creating tests and the concrete elaboration of tests which will form part of the benchmark for scientific understanding.",
    "Ultimately, scientific understanding tests are necessary to analyze, control, and harness the potential of AI in the context of scientific research.",
    "By agents we mean actors who behave according to some set of (partially) internally generated rules.",
    "(partial) Autonomy, interactivity, and adaptability suffice for ascribing agency to an entity (intentionality or freedom are not required)(Jackson & Williams,"
  ]
}